communications.subject: Freedom of Information Act Request: Orpheus AUV Design Process Documents
communications.communication:
To whom it may concern,

Pursuant to the Freedom of Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

Any and all design process documents for Orpheus AUVs. This request is for records generated from August 1, 2017, until December 1, 2022.

The category for this request is Media. I am a journalist with work that has appeared in The Revelator, Sierra, and other publications, and I am requesting this information in that capacity.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request be filled electronically, by email attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your reply to this request within 20 business days, as the statute requires. Please provide a tracking number and an estimated date of completion for the responsive documents.

Sincerely,

Elyse Hauser

communications.subject: Illinois Freedom of Information Act. Request: incident reports
communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Illinois Freedom of Information Act., I hereby request the following records:

all incident reports that happened on march 2025

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 5 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Martin Brooks
